summary: A celestial axe blank object and UV mapped for those who cant do it.
descriptionHtml:
So, another object i created quickly, and i created a rather complex all-in-one UV map...

Yes, i UV mapped it, Yes i will do it in my Following creations, No i wont add textures.

This is just another one of my hand/mind created weapons and again everyone is allowed to use them in their mods, but some credit would be nice.

Still open for suggestions.
author: Ruimtemaatje
